1514
01:07:45,102 --> 01:07:46,520
He'd feel nice, right?

1515
01:07:50,483 --> 01:07:53,069
Man, Si-hyun is so popular.

1516
01:07:53,152 --> 01:07:54,737
Unbelievable.

1517
01:07:57,198 --> 01:08:00,159
THE YELLOW HEART CHIPS
POUR INTO SI-HYUN'S BOX

1518
01:08:00,743 --> 01:08:03,537
<i>And I thought, "I'm going to put some</i>
<i>in Jun-seung's box today too."</i>

