1524
01:08:19,428 --> 01:08:21,222
LAH HYUN-JIN COMPLETED VOTING

1525
01:08:21,305 --> 01:08:23,516
ONE HEART TO JUN-SEUNG
HOW MANY CHIPS TO SI-HYUN?

