01:10:11,832 --> 01:10:13,000
He gave me some again.

1562
01:10:14,043 --> 01:10:16,462
And there were much more than yesterday.

1563
01:10:16,545 --> 01:10:19,256
<i>I could count just with my eyes yesterday,</i>

1564
01:10:19,340 --> 01:10:20,216
<i>but today,</i>

1565
01:10:21,300 --> 01:10:22,843
