1577
01:10:58,254 --> 01:10:59,505
"The meat was delicious."

1578
01:10:59,588 --> 01:11:01,840
"The meat was delicious." "You're funny."

1579
01:11:01,924 --> 01:11:04,343
Look at the period
after the "You're funny."

1580
01:11:04,426 --> 01:11:07,096
You know what's funny?

1581
01:11:07,179 --> 01:11:08,973
Saying someone is funny
after putting in a lot of Heart Chips

1582
01:11:09,056 --> 01:11:11,058
