-Gosh.

1589
01:11:20,442 --> 01:11:22,403
-Hyun-jin is hilarious.
-For real.

1590
01:11:22,486 --> 01:11:25,197
Hyun-jin, you're funny!

1591
01:11:25,281 --> 01:11:27,616
-You're the one that's funny.
-You're the funny one.

1592
01:11:28,701 --> 01:11:31,245
-Man, she is hilarious.
-Seriously.

1593
01:11:31,328 --> 01:11:32,288
<i>You're funny.</i>

1594
