HYUN-JIN GAVE HIM ONE HEART CHIP
HOW MANY DID JI-YOUNG GIVE HIM?

1595
01:11:38,085 --> 01:11:39,086
<i>You're funny.</i>

1596
01:11:40,296 --> 01:11:42,423
Jun-seung is very interesting.

1597
