1620
01:12:48,697 --> 01:12:50,616
<i>So I put ten chips in.</i>

1621
01:12:52,451 --> 01:12:56,288
HYUN-JIN GAVE HIM ONE HEART CIHP
JI-YOUNG GAVE HIM TEN HEART CHIPS

1622
01:12:56,372 --> 01:13:00,125
I think Ji-young is very cautious.

1623
01:13:00,209 --> 01:13:02,669
But she put more Heart Chips in
