1626
01:13:09,760 --> 01:13:12,721
<i>I gave Jun-seung ten Heart Chips,</i>

1627
01:13:13,764 --> 01:13:17,601
<i>and I gave Si-hyun a different amount.</i>

1628
01:13:27,361 --> 01:13:30,447
<i>I was so surprised when I opened the box.</i>

1629
01:13:30,531 --> 01:13:32,908
HOW MANY DID HYUN-JIN GIVE HIM?
JI-YOUNG GAVE HIM 20 HEART CHIPS

1630
01:13:33,492 --> 01:13:36,662
JI-YOUNG GAVE SI-HYUN 20 HEART CHIPS

1631
01:13:37,413 --> 01:13:41,125
<i>Since I didn't expect</i>
<i>Ji-young to give me any,</i>

1632
01:13:41,208 --> 01:13:42,751
it felt like a wave

1633
01:13:43,335 --> 01:13:45,212
