1636
01:13:51,176 --> 01:13:52,386
WE HAVE SO MANY THINGS IN COMMON

1637
01:13:52,469 --> 01:13:54,972
<i>Then, I drew tofu.</i>

1638
01:13:56,348 --> 01:13:57,808
<i>The edge-of-tofu.</i>

1639
01:13:57,891 --> 01:13:58,851
Don't forget.

