1649
01:14:20,247 --> 01:14:21,623
Isn't she charming?

1650
01:14:21,707 --> 01:14:22,958
-She's so cute.
-Yeah.

1651
01:14:25,252 --> 01:14:26,670
<i>"The bathroom is inconvenient."</i>

1652
