How did she even come up with that?

1653
01:14:29,756 --> 01:14:32,301
It was very impactful.

1654
01:14:32,384 --> 01:14:34,011
-He said it was impactful.
-Yeah.

1655
01:14:34,094 --> 01:14:35,220
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

1656
01:14:35,304 --> 01:14:36,680
