about one person.

1683
01:15:47,459 --> 01:15:48,293
Si-hyun is

1684
01:15:48,377 --> 01:15:49,962
-Split.
-split between the two.

1685
01:15:50,045 --> 01:15:51,838
He is really in a dilemma.

1686
01:15:51,922 --> 01:15:56,468
I think I should approach her
