JUN-SEUNG TO JI-YOUNG

1703
01:16:56,528 --> 01:16:59,031
<i>I think I put in the most</i>
<i>this time as well.</i>

1704
01:16:59,865 --> 01:17:00,907
Wait, no.

1705
01:17:01,992 --> 01:17:03,368
