1706
01:17:03,452 --> 01:17:04,745
-Hyun-jin's.
-It isn't him.

1707
01:17:04,828 --> 01:17:05,746
Yes!

1708
01:17:06,538 --> 01:17:08,915
-"The bathroom is inconvenient!"
-Yes!

1709
01:17:08,999 --> 01:17:10,834
-"The bathroom is inconvenient."
-Yes!

1710
