1728
01:18:03,887 --> 01:18:07,432
<i>I saw how many Jun-seung put in mine.</i>

1729
01:18:09,726 --> 01:18:12,771
JUN-SEUNG GAVE HER 76 HEART CHIPS

1730
01:18:13,355 --> 01:18:15,857
That means she put in more
than Jun-seung did.

1731
01:18:19,111 --> 01:18:22,030
HYUN-JIN GAVE HIM 88 HEART CHIPS

1732
01:18:22,614 --> 01:18:23,865
She's a scary lady.

1733
01:18:25,492 --> 01:18:26,952
